xml2ps.pl - gantt chart generator for TaskJuggler


required

    Perl >5.6.x
    XML::Parser
    PostScript::Simple
    Date::Calc
    Class::MethodMaker
    use Data::Dumper        (only for debug)
    Poster                  optional for generate poster
                            http://www.geocities.com/SiliconValley/5682/poster.html

usage

    xml2ps.pl export_from_taskjuggler.xml

output format

    PostScript document text conforming at level 3.0 - type EPS

    <project name>.eps              big gantt one page
    <project name>_poster.eps       big gantt on multiiple page (a4) poster, ready
                                    for printing (require Poster)



